{
  "page": "House of Uhlez",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>House of Uhlez</b> is one of the slaving families of <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a>. \n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_of_Uhlez&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_of_Uhlez&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>The House is hostile to the rule of <a href=\"/index.php/Daenerys_Targaryen\" title=\"Daenerys Targaryen\">Daenerys Targaryen</a> and their household are suspected of being members of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sons_of_the_Harpy\" title=\"Sons of the Harpy\">Sons of the Harpy</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Since the escape of the wild dragons <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegal\" title=\"Rhaegal\">Rhaegal</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Viserion\" title=\"Viserion\">Viserion</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Pyramid_of_Uhlez\" title=\"Pyramid of Uhlez\">pyramid of Uhlez</a> has become the lair of Viserion.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=House_of_Uhlez&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd2.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_2\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 2\">Chapter 2</a>, Daenerys I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd70.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_70\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 70\">Chapter 70</a>, The Queen's Hand.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing:0;;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding:2px;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"nowraplinks hlist collapsible autocollapse navbox-inner\" style=\"border-spacing:0;background:transparent;width:100%;color:inherit;;;\"><tbody><tr><th scope=\"col\" style=\";\" class=\"navbox-title\" colspan=\"2\"><div class=\"plainlinks hlist\" style=\"display:block;float:left;font-weight:normal;font-size:88%;padding-top:3px;text-align:left;width:6.8em;\"><ul><li class=\"nv-view\"><a href=\"/